WEBVTT

0
00:00:02.769 --> 00:00:06.762
I'm Peppa Pig.This
is my little brother, George.

1
00:00:07.574 --> 00:00:08.506
This is Mummy Pig.

2
00:00:09.909 --> 00:00:11.001
And this is Daddy Pig.

3
00:00:13.413 --> 00:00:14.505
Peppa pig.

4
00:00:19.919 --> 00:00:21.853
Cleaning the Car!

5
00:00:26.292 --> 00:00:27.520
Daddy Pig is taking the family

6
00:00:27.594 --> 00:00:28.583
for a drive in the country.

7
00:00:29.162 --> 00:00:31.528
Come on!
ls everyone ready?

8
00:00:32.432 --> 00:00:33.364
Ready!

9
00:00:34.367 --> 00:00:36.301
Yes, Daddy Pig, We're ready.

10
00:00:37.303 --> 00:00:38.861
But the car isn't ready!

11
00:00:39.305 --> 00:00:40.533
Look how messy it is!

12
00:00:42.542 --> 00:00:44.305
Oh, it's not too bad.

13
00:00:44.677 --> 00:00:47.237
You should see how
messy it is inside!

14
00:00:48.181 --> 00:00:48.943
Oh!

15
00:00:49.182 --> 00:00:51.173
Naughty, messy Daddy!

16
00:00:52.252 --> 00:00:54.311
Naughty, messy Daddy!

17
00:00:56.256 --> 00:00:59.248
Look at all this rubbish!
Newspapers!

18
00:00:59.959 --> 00:01:00.823
They're mine.

19
00:01:01.461 --> 00:01:02.257
Sweets!

20
00:01:02.562 --> 00:01:03.620
They're mine!

21
00:01:03.963 --> 00:01:06.693
Mr. Dinosaur!
Dine-saw! Grrrr!

22
00:01:09.135 --> 00:01:12.070
We must clean the car
before We go for a drive.

23
00:01:12.338 --> 00:01:14.704
Oh, right you are, Mummy Pig.

24
00:01:14.841 --> 00:01:16.706
Mummy, can We help to clean the car?

25
00:01:17.844 --> 00:01:18.970
Yes, if you Want to.

26
00:01:19.145 --> 00:01:20.339
Hurray!

27
00:01:23.082 --> 00:01:25.414
Daddy Pig has some Warm
soapy Water to Wash the car.

28
00:01:29.589 --> 00:01:30.715
Daddy pig
is Washing the roof.

29
00:01:32.792 --> 00:01:34.350
Mummy Pig is
Washing the bonnet.

30
00:01:36.229 --> 00:01:37.355
Peppa is Washing the doors.

31
00:01:39.732 --> 00:01:41.165
George Wants to Wash the Windows.

32
00:01:42.602 --> 00:01:43.864
But he is too little.

33
00:01:45.872 --> 00:01:47.863
Poor George. Let me help you.

34
00:01:54.447 --> 00:01:56.005
Oh, dear! George has
dropped his sponge

35
00:01:56.182 --> 00:01:57.114
in a muddy puddle.

36
00:02:01.621 --> 00:02:05.113
George, you're making the
car all muddy again!

37
00:02:09.128 --> 00:02:10.686
I Will Wash the mud off.

38
00:02:11.831 --> 00:02:16.268
Peppa, don't use the...muddy Water.

39
00:02:18.705 --> 00:02:20.340
Oh, dear! Peppa has thrown
the muddy Water

40
00:02:20.340 --> 00:02:21.329
all over the car.

41
00:02:22.542 --> 00:02:23.338
Oh.

42
00:02:24.277 --> 00:02:24.971
Never mind.

43
00:02:25.278 --> 00:02:26.973
We can use the garden
hose to clean it off.

44
00:02:27.547 --> 00:02:30.641
Yes! Yes!
Can I hold the hose?

45
00:02:38.658 --> 00:02:41.855
Peppa holds the hose and
Daddy Pig turns on the Water.

46
00:02:45.665 --> 00:02:50.932
Where's the Water?
Wahhh!

47
00:02:53.740 --> 00:02:55.674
Arrgh! Peppa! Stop!

48
00:02:56.175 --> 00:02:57.164
Sorry, Mummy.

49
00:03:00.380 --> 00:03:01.005
Oh.

50
00:03:01.514 --> 00:03:05.245
Argh! Daddy Pig! Please
turn off the Water!

51
00:03:05.952 --> 00:03:09.388
Oh! No need to panic.

52
00:03:12.091 --> 00:03:13.956
Oh, dear, everyone is Wet.

53
00:03:15.828 --> 00:03:17.386
At least the
car has been Washed.

54
00:03:17.597 --> 00:03:19.189
We've all been Washed.

55
00:03:21.534 --> 00:03:24.025
You go and dry yourselves
While I polish the car.

56
00:03:24.470 --> 00:03:25.459
See you later.

57
00:03:25.705 --> 00:03:26.603
See you later.

58
00:03:35.715 --> 00:03:37.478
Daddy Pig is polishing
the car so Well,

59
00:03:37.917 --> 00:03:39.214
he can see his face in it.

60
00:03:43.423 --> 00:03:44.549
What a funny face!

61
00:03:45.858 --> 00:03:47.416
Oh! More funny faces!

62
00:03:48.861 --> 00:03:50.123
It's Peppa and George!

63
00:03:51.064 --> 00:03:51.996
And Mummy Pig.

64
00:03:52.632 --> 00:03:54.793
What a Iovely, shiny car.

65
00:03:55.501 --> 00:03:58.231
Yes, I am a bit of an
expert at these things.

66
00:04:00.573 --> 00:04:02.063
Come on, I'll drive today.

67
00:04:02.742 --> 00:04:03.868
ls everybody ready?

68
00:04:04.077 --> 00:04:04.941
Ready!

69
00:04:06.379 --> 00:04:07.744
Then lets go!

70
00:04:14.387 --> 00:04:16.947
I hope you Will all keep
this car clean today.

71
00:04:17.090 --> 00:04:18.148
Yes, Mummy Pig.

72
00:04:18.391 --> 00:04:19.517
Yes, Mummy Pig.

73
00:04:23.262 --> 00:04:24.251
Arrgh!

74
00:04:27.767 --> 00:04:31.328
Mummy, now you've made
the car all muddy again.

75
00:04:32.972 --> 00:04:34.269
Naughty Mummy.

76
00:04:35.174 --> 00:04:37.165
Naughty, messy Mummy.

